.TH MPE_Make_color_array 4 "12/24/1994" " " "MPE"
.SH NAME
MPE_Make_color_array \- Makes an array of color indices

.SH INPUT PARAMETERS
.PD 0
.TP
.B handle 
- MPE graphics handle
.PD 1
.PD 0
.TP
.B nc 
- Number of colors
.PD 1

.SH OUTPUT PARAMETER
.PD 0
.TP
.B array 
- Array of color indices
.PD 1

.SH NOTES
The new colors for a uniform distribution in hue space and replace the
existing colors EXCEPT for MPE_WHITE and MPE_BLACK.
.SH SYNOPSIS
.nf
#include <stdio.h>
